<h4>Businesses</h4><h5>Carmarthenshire</h5><div class="error">Carmarthenshire County Council The Council hosts information on potential sources of funding for a wide range of businesses in its 'Supporting Businesses' hub: http://newsroom.carmarthenshire.gov.wales/2020/03/coronavirus/supporting-businesses-coronavirus-covid-19/#.XsTXDBpKhyw</div><h5>Guidance</h5><p>Some advice for small businesses from a <a href="http://www.lhphillips.com/small-business-emergency-action-plan/">a local firm of accountants</a></p><h4>Wales</h4><h5>Business Wales</h5><p>For information on <a href="https://businesswales.gov.wales/coronavirus-advice/">grants and support to Welsh businesses, employees, and self-employed people</a></p><h5>Community Foundation Wales</h5>The <a href="http://communityfoundationwales.org.uk/grants/wales-coronavirus-resilience-fund/">Coronavirus Resilience Fund</a> has been established to assist groups and organisations that are adapting their services and support to individuals and families, whether singly or collectively, affected by the Coronavirus pandemic.<h5>Farmers</h5><p>New funding to support Welsh dairy farmers announced by the Welsh Government Rural Affairs Minister. Details to be published soon. The announcement can be found here: <a href="https://gov.wales/new-funding-to-support-welsh-dairy-farmers-through-covid-19">https://gov.wales/new-funding-to-support-welsh-dairy-farmers-through-covid-19</a></p><h5>Welsh Government</h5><p>There are further links available to sources of advice, funding, and support for businesses and employers on the Welsh Government website: <a href="https://gov.wales/business-and-employers-coronavirus">https://gov.wales/business-and-employers-coronavirus</a></p><h4>UK Government</h4><h5>General Support</h5><p>Range of links: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/coronavirus/business-support">https://www.gov.uk/coronavirus/business-support</a></p><h5>Self-Employment</h5><p>Self-employment grants under the UK scheme: <a href="http://www.gov.uk/guidance/claim-a-grant-through-the-coronavirus-covid-19-self-employment-income-support-scheme">www.gov.uk/guidance/claim-a-grant-through-the-coronavirus-covid-19-self-employment-income-support-scheme</a></p>